        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Fossil 专注传统钟表产品，宣布撤出 Wear OS 智能手表市场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/fossil-wear-os-smartwatch-business-exit/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fossil-wear-os-smartwatch-business-exit</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/fossil-wear-os-smartwatch-business-exit/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fossil]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fossil Gen 6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Wear OS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217682</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>自从钟表品牌 Fossil 在 2021 年 8 月发表搭载 Wear OS 系统的 Gen 6 智能手表系列后，外界在过去两年半一直期待 Gen 7 的消息，期间 Fossil 只在 2022 年底为 Gen 6 推出过 Wellness 版，规格配置维持不变，唯一不同就是系统版本由之前的 Wear OS 2.0 升级至 3.0。</p><p><span id="more-1217682"></span></p><p>去年底有外国媒体报导指 Fossil 将停止推出 Wear OS 智能手表，而公司亦开始为多款智能手表提供大幅度折扣，似乎是要清理库存。如今 Fossil 终于对外确认退出智能手表业务，在回应网站 The Verge 的查询时，集团发言人 Amanda Castelli 表示近年智能手表市场出现重大变化，致令他们作出退出智能手表业务的决定。Fossil 会将资源重新调拨去支持具有优势的核心业务部门，包括设计、分销自家和授权品牌的传统手表、珠宝和皮具，去把握强劲的增长势头。</p><p>虽然 Fossil 决定退出智能手表市场，但他们承诺将继续为现有的 Wear OS 智能手表提供更新。自从 Google 在 Wear OS 研发找来 Samsung 合作，后者就一直拥有优势，能够比起其他厂商更早预载和更新 Wear OS 的最新版本，以去年 7 月随 Galaxy Watch6 系列发表的 Wear OS 4 为例，其他厂商至今还未能预载和更新，只有 Google Pixel Watch 例外。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/fossil_wear_os_smartwatch_business_exit-news-61378.php">gsmarena</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/25/fossil-no-longer-release-new-wear-os-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">与 Google 合作关系告一段落，传钟表集团 Fossil 将弃用 Wear OS 系统</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/30/fossil-gen-6-receive-wear-os-3-5-update/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Fossil Gen 6 系统升级   Wear OS 3.5 效能提升续航改善</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/fossil-wear-os-smartwatch-business-exit/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/">Fossil 专注传统钟表产品，宣布撤出 Wear OS 智能手表市场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
